"@sofiaiskates is a Junior Lady training in Colorado Springs. She grew up skating in Los Angeles. This piece is about coming back to her roots and revisiting places and memories of her past. In the end realizing all the moments and experiences she's been through has led her to where she is today." - Choreographer @crystalrose.sanders
❄️
I also grew up skating in Los Angeles, and I relocated to train for most of my competitive career in Michigan. Coach Crystal is one of my oldest skating friends from the Culver City Ice Arena days. It's super fitting that we got together to film this piece with Sofia in our hometown last month. Sofia learned this choreography completely the day before we shot it! Great job!
__🎥 by Jordan @oniceperspectives
__⛸ @sofiaiskates 
__👣 @crystalrose.sanders
__🎵 Hometown Glory @adele
